# My_favorite_pizza_dough

Creator: Spilled Beans

## Solution

1. Base64 decode
1. Braile to text
1. ROT13 decrypt
1. Take the hex string
1. Hex decode
1. XOR bruteforce

CyberChef recipe:
https://gchq.github.io/CyberChef/#recipe=From_Base64('A-Za-z0-9%2B/%3D',true,false)From_Braille()ROT13(true,true,false,13)Subsection('.%2B$',true,true,false)From_Hex('Auto')XOR_Brute_Force(1,100,0,'Standard',false,false,false,'TSRY%7B')&
